{
  "info": {
    "name": "Image Processing API - Challenge",
    "_postman_id": "challenge-api-collection",
    "description": "Colección completa para probar la API REST de procesado de imágenes.\n\n**Configuración:**\n1. La API debe estar corriendo en http://localhost:8000\n2. MongoDB debe estar disponible\n3. Importa esta colección en Postman\n4. Actualiza la variable `imagePath` con una ruta válida\n\n**Casos de Uso Incluidos:**\n- Crear tarea de procesamiento\n- Consultar estado de tarea (pending/completed)\n- Manejo de errores (404)\n- Verificar generación de precio aleatorio",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Tasks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Crear Tarea - Imagen Local",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code es 201\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Respuesta contiene taskId\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('taskId');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.taskId).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"lastTaskId\", jsonData.taskId);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Estado inicial es 'pending'\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.equal('pending');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Precio está asignado entre 5 y 50\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('price');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.price).to.be.at.least(5);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.price).to.be.at.most(50);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"No contiene images en estado pending\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.images).to.be.undefined;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"imagePath\": \"{{imagePath}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tasks"]
            },
            "description": "Crea una nueva tarea de procesamiento de imagen.\n\n**Input:**\n- `imagePath`: Ruta local o URL de la imagen a procesar\n\n**Output:**\n- `taskId`: ID único de la tarea\n- `status`: Estado inicial (pending)\n- `price`: Precio aleatorio entre 5 y 50\n\n**Nota:** El procesamiento se ejecuta de forma asíncrona. La tarea se crea inmediatamente en estado pending."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Respuesta exitosa",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"imagePath\": \"/path/to/image.jpg\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["tasks"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"taskId\": \"65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6\",\n  \"status\": \"pending\",\n  \"price\": 25.5\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Consultar Tarea - Estado Pending",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code es 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Respuesta contiene estructura correcta\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('taskId');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('status');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('price');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Precio es consistente\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.price).to.be.at.least(5);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.price).to.be.at.most(50);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{lastTaskId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tasks", "{{lastTaskId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta el estado de una tarea recién creada (normalmente en estado pending).\n\n**Output (pending):**\n- `taskId`: ID de la tarea\n- `status`: pending\n- `price`: Precio asignado\n\n**Nota:** Ejecuta este request inmediatamente después de crear una tarea para verla en estado pending."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Tarea en estado pending",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks/65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["tasks", "65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"taskId\": \"65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6\",\n  \"status\": \"pending\",\n  \"price\": 25.5\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Consultar Tarea - Estado Completed",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code es 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Estado es 'completed'\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.equal('completed');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Contiene array de images\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('images');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.images).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Se generaron 2 resoluciones (1024 y 800)\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.images).to.have.lengthOf(2);",
                  "    ",
                  "    var resolutions = jsonData.images.map(img => img.resolution);",
                  "    pm.expect(resolutions).to.include('1024');",
                  "    pm.expect(resolutions).to.include('800');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Cada imagen tiene resolution y path\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    jsonData.images.forEach(function(image) {",
                  "        pm.expect(image).to.have.property('resolution');",
                  "        pm.expect(image).to.have.property('path');",
                  "        pm.expect(image.path).to.include('/output/');",
                  "        pm.expect(image.path).to.include('/' + image.resolution + '/');",
                  "    });",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{lastTaskId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tasks", "{{lastTaskId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta el estado de una tarea después de que ha sido procesada.\n\n**Output (completed):**\n- `taskId`: ID de la tarea\n- `status`: completed\n- `price`: Precio asignado\n- `images`: Array con las variantes generadas\n  - `resolution`: Ancho en pixels (1024 o 800)\n  - `path`: Ruta del archivo generado\n\n**Nota:** Espera unos segundos después de crear la tarea antes de ejecutar este request para ver el estado completed."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Tarea completada con imágenes",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tasks/65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["tasks", "65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"taskId\": \"65d4a54b89c5e342b2c2c5f6\",\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"price\": 25.5,\n  \"images\": [\n    {\n      \"resolution\": \"1024\",\n      \"path\": \"/output/image1/1024/f322b730b287da77e1c519c7ffef4fc2.jpg\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"resolution\": \"800\",\n      \"path\": \"/output/image1/800/202fd8b3174a774bac24428e8cb230a1.jpg\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
